modShortDescription: This mod will prevent trees from growing, and prevent the servers from being full of blue spruce tree.
modDescription:
This mod will prevent [trees](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-trees/) from growing, and prevent the servers from being full of blue spruce tree. Principle: Let the next growth stage of seedlings become seedlings!

**[Download](https://docs.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1ncXdemGE12eDSBACwPwhluL_jRlydABY)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/22921-a19bbbbillys-practical-mods-collection/).

**Credits:** [BBBBilly](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/bbbbilly/)
